'''Steve Eboh''', uzwi cyane nka '''Ajebo''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Nijeriya|Nigeriya]] . <ref>https://www.happenings.com.ng/latest/2020/01/23/actors-are-more-concerned-about-makeup-than-their-roles-steve-eboh</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwa firime ''Igipimo Cyinshi'', ''Igipimo Cyinshi 2'' na ''Lionheart'' . Usibye gukina, Eboh numuproducer, umuntu wa tereviziyo numugiraneza. <ref>https://www.pinterest.com/pin/155514993368244417/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Ni indigene ya Achi muri Oji River LGA yo muri leta ya Enugu. Nyuma yaje kurangiza afite impamyabumenyi y'itumanaho muri Kaminuza ya Lagos. <ref name="sunnewsonline">https://www.sunnewsonline.com/domestic-oil-firm-picks-nollywoods-steve-eboh-as-brand-ambassador/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Muri 1996, yakinnye bwa mbere muri firime yo murugo ''Karishika'' hamwe na ''Karishika 2 yayo'' . Kuva icyo gihe yakomeje kwiganza muri firime nyinshi zo murugo. Yakinnye muri firime nyinshi zizwi nka Nollywood nka ''Taboo'', ''Ikuku'', ''Narrow Escape'', ''Ibibi bibi'' na ''Concubines'' . <ref name="sunnewsonline" /> Muri 2018, yagaragaye muri firime yo murugo ''Lionheart'' afite uruhare runini. <ref>https://media.dream13.com/lionheart-2018/</ref> <ref>https://thewhistler.ng/genevieves-lionheart-set-to-premiere-in-toronto-film-festival/</ref>

Muri kamena 2019, Eboh yatangajwe nka ambasaderi w’ikirango cya sosiyete itanga peteroli na Nigeriya yitwa 'GOVOIL'.  Hagati aho, yabaye Visi Perezida w’ishyirahamwe ry’abakinnyi muri Nijeriya (AGN), na Perezida wa Komite y’igihugu ishinzwe kwita ku bana, AGN. <ref>https://www.pressreader.com/nigeria/thisday/20200219/282089163790319</ref> Yabaye kandi umuyobozi mukuru wa Confirm Projects International Ltd mugihe gito. <ref>https://www.today.ng/culture/film/nollywood-committee-pledges-credible-election-actors-guild-258443</ref>

